{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e3860fffd5","title":"在“五一”节中南海晚会上的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"335d9fd0f2","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":1,"articleId":"e3860fffd5"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3bff1d2fc6","name":"暴力和武斗","type":"主题"},{"id":"5387dec24b","name":"文学艺术","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c11a1a00ba","type":"title","text":"在“五一”节中南海晚会上的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e3860fffd5"},{"id":"3df0774b93","type":"paragraph","text":"（毛泽东听到江青介绍京剧团有人被打的事后）毛泽东（以下简称毛）：现在还打不打了？演员：现在我们都团结一致了。毛：不打了，好。毛：现在还有没有反二簧、反西皮演员：在革命现代戏中，反二簧、反西皮可不可以用？毛：我看可以用","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e3860fffd5"}],"page":{"id":"aebc286e14","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e3860fffd5","start":449,"end":449}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0139b462db","type":"paragraph","text":"毛还问了谭富英一些老演员的情况。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e3860fffd5"},{"id":"2256c16e58","type":"paragraph","text":"毛说：“不打了，好！”","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e3860fffd5"},{"id":"25baa7f19d","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.05.01","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e3860fffd5"},{"id":"421efecc0f","type":"paragraph","text":"在演唱中，毛问：“现在还有没有反二簧，反西皮？”演员们说：“在革命现代戏中，反二簧，反西皮可不可以用？”毛说“我看可以用。”","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e3860fffd5"},{"id":"435d75f5e1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e3860fffd5"},{"id":"666a288db1","type":"title","text":"在“五一”节中南海晚会上的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e3860fffd5"},{"id":"8678b7012f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛听到江青介绍京剧一团有人被打的事后，问：“现在还打不打了。”答：“现在我们都团结一致了。”","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e3860fffd5"},{"id":"f7f9d06244","type":"paragraph","text":"在“五一”节中南海晚会上的谈话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e3860fffd5"}],"page":{"id":"23f3ef4bc8","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e3860fffd5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}